Waterloo Mayor Ted Young told CNY that he has contact Barto's family and that his condition seems  to be improving. 

'This is an incident that hits right close to home,' Young said. 'He's one of our employees, well known and liked in the village. We're concerned about how something like this can happen and why it happened.'

